snippet: The police found no weapon in the car of a Connecticut woman who was killed by officers after trying to ram her vehicle through a White House barrier, court papers said.
abstract: Police find no weapon or evidence of motive while searching car of Miriam Carey,  Connecticut woman who was fatally shot by officers after trying to ram her vehicle through White House barrier.
lead_paragraph: The police found no weapon in the car of a Connecticut woman who was killed by officers after trying to ram her vehicle through a White House barrier, court papers said.

headline.main: Car Search Yields No Clues in Fatal Chase
headline.print_headline: Car Search Yields No Clues In Fatal Chase
